text: Simone Budde (born 2 January 1979) is a German water polo player. She was part of the Germany women's national water polo team at the 2003 World Aquatics Championships, 2007 World Aquatics Championships, and 2009 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Simone Budde - Simone Budde Photos - Zimbio Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:German water polo players
